title: New Girl - Complete Season 4 S04 - 720p - x265
description:
As for the first (https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/15637341), second (https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/15724367) and third (https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/15759873) seasons, don't expect the full quality of beautiful HD but rather "better than SD for ~half the size".

Converted from https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/13944457/New_Girl_S04_Season_4_Complete_1080p_WEB-DL_[MIXED] and let's be honest, this release was a mess. Seriously. Why keeping the F0x ads ? But this one had already the subtitles, so it was a little better.

So, I converted the audio to AAC 2.0 and removed those AWEFUL pre and post-roll F0x ads on each episodes).

Anyway, as always, don't hesitate to give me any suggestion.
I will (probably) do the last season in the coming weeks.
